'''2020－2021年印度农民抗议活动'''是印度農民針對[[印度议会|印度议会]]於2020年9月通過的三項農業法案（《2020農產品貿易和商業（促進和便利）法案》、《2020農民（授權和保護）價格保證協議和農業服務法案》和《2020基本商品（修正）法案》<ref>{{cite news |title=印度新德里周边发生大规模农民抗议 冲突或持续升级 |url=http://news.cri.cn/20201127/5608cbf6-328b-af83-79ad-4a96f16baac0.html |publisher=國際在線}}</ref>）而進行的持续抗议活动<ref>Vaibhav Palnitkar (21 September 2020). [https://www.thequint.com/news/india/farmers-protesting-the-3-new-ordinances Why farmers protesting against 3 new Ordinances] {{Wayback|url=https://www.thequint.com/news/india/farmers-protesting-the-3-new-ordinances |date=20201031113722 }}. ''The Quint''. Retrieved 28 October 2020.</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Gettleman|first=Jeffrey|author2=Singh|first2=Karan Deep|last3=Kumar|first3=Hari|date=2020-11-30|title=Angry Farmers Choke India’s Capital in Giant Demonstrations|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/30/world/asia/india-farmers-protest.html|accessdate=2020-12-01|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201005737/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/30/world/asia/india-farmers-protest.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=‘Ordinance to put farmers at mercy of corporates’|url=https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/punjab/ordinance-to-put-farmers-at-mercy-of-corporates-99720|accessdate=2020-12-02|author=|date=2020-06-15|first=|work=Tribuneindia News Service|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211211443/https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/punjab/ordinance-to-put-farmers-at-mercy-of-corporates-99720|archivedate=2020-12-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Now, farmers will be back to serfdom, at the mercy of big corporates: Manish Tewari|url=https://www.deccanherald.com/national/national-politics/now-farmers-will-be-back-to-serfdom-at-the-mercy-of-big-corporates-manish-tewari-891010.html|accessdate=2020-12-02|date=2020-09-22|work=Deccan Herald|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201006071235/https://www.deccanherald.com/national/national-politics/now-farmers-will-be-back-to-serfdom-at-the-mercy-of-big-corporates-manish-tewari-891010.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據新法案，印度政府允許大型私有企業進入農產品銷售市場，並允許商家囤積食品。在這些法案出台後不久，印度各地就出現抗议活动，農民擔心大型企業進入糧食市場會壓低糧食價格，使得印度政府不再以保證價格從農民手中收購糧食<ref>{{cite news |title=印度农业法改革恐冲击粮食收购保证价格，农民占领道路抗议 |url=https://3g.163.com/dy/article/FNF8NP5T0514R9P4.html |publisher=澎湃新闻}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=印度农民抗议使莫迪政府不安 |url=https://chinese.aljazeera.net/gallery/2020/12/1/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%86%9C%E6%B0%91%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE%E4%BD%BF%E8%8E%AB%E8%BF%AA%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%89 |publisher=半島電視台 |accessdate=2020-12-05 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202030215/https://chinese.aljazeera.net/gallery/2020/12/1/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%86%9C%E6%B0%91%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE%E4%BD%BF%E8%8E%AB%E8%BF%AA%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%89 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。抗議活動規模最大的就要數[[旁遮普邦|旁遮普邦]]和[[哈里亚纳邦|哈里亚纳邦]]舉行的抗議。

== 歷史 ==
抗議爆發2個月後，旁遮普邦和哈里亞納邦的農民還發起了一場名為 "Delhi Chalo"（讓我們去德里）的運動，數万農民向印度首都[[新德里|新德里]]進發。警察和執法部門使用水砲和催淚瓦斯阻止農民湧入[[德里|德里]]<ref name=":5">{{Cite web|title=What agitating farmers want, and why the Centre may not oblige|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/india-today-insight/story/what-agitating-farmers-want-and-why-the-centre-may-not-oblige-1745475-2020-11-30|accessdate=2020-12-03|author=Mahajan|date=2020-11-30|first=Anilesh S.|work=India Today|language=en|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20201206214202/https://www.indiatoday.in/india-today-insight/story/what-agitating-farmers-want-and-why-the-centre-may-not-oblige-1745475-2020-11-30|archivedate=2020-12-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2020年12月5日，共有超過2億農民走上街頭，並封鎖印度各地通往首都新德里的高速公路入口<ref>{{Cite web|title=India Sees The Largest Protest In Human History - YouTube|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HZUR9KAbxLk&feature=youtu.be|access-date=2020-12-05|website=www.youtube.com|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204215831/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HZUR9KAbxLk&feature=youtu.be|dead-url=no}}</ref>￼。

農民工會及其代表要求廢除或修改相關法律，並表示不接受妥協。<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=15 January 2021|title=Farm laws stir: Talks with Centre '120% fail', say farmer leaders; next round on January 19|url=https://scroll.in/latest/984158/farm-laws-stir-talks-with-centre-120-fail-say-farmer-leaders-next-round-on-january-19|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115152155/https://scroll.in/latest/984158/farm-laws-stir-talks-with-centre-120-fail-say-farmer-leaders-next-round-on-january-19|archive-date=2021-01-15 |access-date=2021-01-15|website=Scroll.in|language=en-US}}</ref>

2021年1月22日，印度農業部長表示，印度政府不會廢除三項農業法案，但是表示可以將法律實施時間延後18個月。农民對印度农业部长的表態不滿，要求徹底廢除三項農業法案。1月26日，當天為[[印度共和國日|印度共和國日]]，印度農民在新德里舉行拖拉機抗議遊行，並衝破路障和警察發生衝突，在衝突中一名農民身亡<ref>{{cite news |title=印度农民举行拖拉机抗议游行 与警方发生激烈冲突 |url=https://www.yicai.com/news/100929145.html |accessdate=2021-01-27 |archive-date=2021-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131064023/https://www.yicai.com/news/100929145.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2021年11月19日，印度总理莫迪决定废止三項農業法案。<ref>{{cite news |title=莫迪决定撤销引发农民强烈抗议的三部农业法 |url=https://www.zaobao.com.sg/realtime/world/story20211119-1214994 |accessdate=2021-11-19 |archive-date=2021-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211204010743/https://www.zaobao.com.sg/realtime/world/story20211119-1214994 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
== 網絡審查 ==
大量示威者在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上討論事件，2021年2月1日[[印度電子信息技術部|印度電子信息技術部]]要求Twitter封鎖250個賬號和推文，Twitter封禁數十個賬號十二小時，包括一些知名人士的賬號<ref>{{cite news |author1=Manish Singh |title=Twitter restricts numerous high-profile accounts in India following ‘legal demand’ [Update] |url=https://techcrunch.com/2021/02/01/twitter-restricts-over-a-dozen-high-profile-accounts-in-india-following-legal-demand/ |accessdate=2021-05-08 |work=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]] |date=2021-02-01 |language=en |archive-date=2021-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210526005223/https://techcrunch.com/2021/02/01/twitter-restricts-over-a-dozen-high-profile-accounts-in-india-following-legal-demand/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之後[[印度電子信息技術部|印度電子信息技術部]]根據《{{link-en|信息技術法 (2000年)|Information Technology Act, 2000|信息技術法}}》69A對Twitter及其高管發出警告，如不處理相關内容將面臨[[有期徒刑|有期徒刑]]和罰款。2月10日Twitter和印度電子信息技術部召開網上會議，同日印度發佈新聞稿指責Twitter在處理[[2021年美国国会大厦遭冲击事件|2021年美国国会大厦遭冲击事件]]和[[德里红堡|德里红堡]]騷動時有區別對待之疑。隨即Twitter應要求封鎖500個賬號，絕大部分為永久封禁，以防止印度農民抗議等相關字眼出現在Twitter趨勢上<ref>{{cite news |author1=Manish Singh |title=Twitter suspends over 500 accounts in India after government warning |url=https://techcrunch.com/2021/02/09/twitter-takes-actions-on-over-500-accounts-in-india-amid-government-warning/ |accessdate=2021-05-08 |work=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]] |date=2021-02-10 |language=en |archive-date=2021-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210606095016/https://techcrunch.com/2021/02/09/twitter-takes-actions-on-over-500-accounts-in-india-amid-government-warning/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 評價 ==
爆發抗議後，前世行首席經濟學家卡西克·巴蘇（Kaushik Basu）站在農民一邊，與[[纳伦德拉·莫迪|納倫德拉·莫迪]]的經濟顧問、前亞行首席經濟學家阿文德·帕納加里亞（Arvind Panagariya）辩论。<ref>{{cite news |author1=TOI |title=New Farms laws 2020: 3 Experts, 2 Opinions - Times of India |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/farms-laws-3-experts-2-opinions/articleshow/79790878.cms |accessdate=2021-01-12 |work=The Times of India |agency=Times of India |date=2020-12-18 |archive-date=2020-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220035251/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/farms-laws-3-experts-2-opinions/articleshow/79790878.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>哈佛學者李漢松認為，印度農業商品化過程中配套風險緩釋機制不足，此次危機反映的是印度“社會凝聚力和公信力的匱乏”。<ref>{{cite news |author1=Ian Neubauer |title=Indian farmers protesting against challenging conditions |url=https://thefarmermagazine.com.au/why-are-indian-farmers-protesting/ |accessdate=2021-08-11 |work=The Farmer Magazine |date=2021-05-24 |language=en-AU |archive-date=2021-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210811155915/https://thefarmermagazine.com.au/why-are-indian-farmers-protesting/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=李汉松 |title=2020︱动荡一年中的三个历史片段_私家历史_澎湃新闻-The Paper |url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_10533964 |website=www.thepaper.cn |publisher=澎湃 |accessdate=2021-01-12 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113213905/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_10533964 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

